    <item>
      <title>耶伦赞扬哈里斯，呼吁美国继续发挥全球领导作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/yellen-lauds-harris-calls-for-continued-us-global-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特·耶伦对美国在11月大选后退出国际参与的风险发出警告，并称赞副总统卡马拉·哈里斯是一位欣赏美国全球领导力的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/yellen-lauds-harris-calls-for-continued-us-global-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 16:22:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普取得进展 哈里斯呼吁工会参与 2024 年竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/harris-appeals-to-unions-in-2024-blitz-as-trump-makes-inroads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为 2024 年总统候选人，卡马拉·哈里斯首次直接向工会工人推销自己的竞选策略，试图锁定一个她无法承受叛逃的宝贵选区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/harris-appeals-to-unions-in-2024-blitz-as-trump-makes-inroads</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 16:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中印同意“紧急”解决边界争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/china-and-india-agree-to-resolve-border-dispute-with-urgency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和印度同意“紧急”合作解决长达四年之久的边界争端，这一争端阻碍了这两个南亚邻国关系的正常化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/china-and-india-agree-to-resolve-border-dispute-with-urgency</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:47:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将参加东非反恐演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/china-to-take-part-in-counter-terrorism-drills-in-east-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防部发言人张晓刚表示，中国军队将于本月晚些时候与莫桑比克、坦桑尼亚参加联合反恐演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/china-to-take-part-in-counter-terrorism-drills-in-east-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽森将下令加州拆除无家可归者的营地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/newsom-set-to-order-california-to-remove-homeless-encampments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）发布命令，要求拆除美国无家可归者最多的州内的无家可归者营地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/newsom-set-to-order-california-to-remove-homeless-encampments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:25:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>六名众议院民主党人投票谴责哈里斯的边境政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/six-house-democrats-vote-to-condemn-harris-on-border-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，六名摇摆选区的众议院民主党人与共和党人一起投票谴责副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的政府打击非法移民的表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/six-house-democrats-vote-to-condemn-harris-on-border-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国支持加拿大填补中国电动汽车“漏洞”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-backs-canada-moving-to-close-chinese-electric-car-loophole</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻加拿大大使表示，有迹象表明贾斯汀·特鲁多总理领导的政府正在堵塞“漏洞”，这一漏洞可能允许中国支持的电动汽车通过加拿大进入美国，从而避开关税，这令他感到鼓舞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-backs-canada-moving-to-close-chinese-electric-car-loophole</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:01:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 将在市场斗争中受到欧盟反垄断命令的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/meta-set-to-be-hit-by-eu-antitrust-order-in-marketplace-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 因被控将 Facebook Marketplace 与其社交网络捆绑在一起，滥用其在分类广告市场的主导地位，面临欧盟的首次罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/meta-set-to-be-hit-by-eu-antitrust-order-in-marketplace-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
